For solutions of this equation in integer values of formula_30 see here.

The altitude from either leg coincides with the other leg. Since these intersect at the right-angled vertex, the right triangle&#x27;s orthocenter—the intersection of its three altitudes—coincides with the right-angled vertex.

===Inradius and circumradius===
The radius of the incircle of a right triangle with legs formula_2 and formula_5 and hypotenuse formula_1 is
